{{defn|Initials of Atiyah, Drinfeld, Hitchin, and Manin, as in the [[ADHM construction]] of instantons.}}

{{term|ADM}}
{{defn|Initials of Arnowitt, Deser, and Misner, as in [[ADM energy]], a way of defining the global energy in an asymptotically flat spacetime, or [[ADM decomposition]] of a metric, or [[ADM formalism]].}}

{{term|AdS}}
{{defn|Anti-de Sitter, as in [[anti-de Sitter space]], a Lorentzian analogue of hyperbolic space}}

{{term|AdS/CFT}}
