{{term|axino}}
{{defn|{{main|Axino}} A hypothetical supersymmetric partner of an axion.}}

{{term|axion}}
{{defn|{{main|Axion}} A hypothetical scalar particle whose mass arises from a coupling rather than from a mass term in the Lagrangian, used to resolve the [[strong CP problem]].}}

